filtlong
------------------------------------------
Quality filtering of long noisy DNA sequencing reads

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.10-1
  libgcc1-14.4.0-1
  libstdc++6-14.4.0-1
  zlib0-1.3.2-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-14.4.0-1
  make-4.4.1-2
  python39-3.9.16-1
  zlib-devel-1.3.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/rrwick/Filtlong

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/rrwick/Filtlong/archive/refs/tags/v0.3.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack filtlong-0.3.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./filtlong-0.3.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/filtlong-0.3.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/filtlong-0.3.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(filtlong)
  /usr/bin/filtlong.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/filtlong.README
  /usr/share/doc/filtlong/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/filtlong/README.md

